data.description: Explore the ideal fusion of coziness and safety in this newly remodeled delightful 3-bedroom townhouse. It features a main bedroom on the ground floor for easy access.. The townhome also includes a 2-car garage, providing plenty of room for both parking and storage. Residents will appreciate the community’s amenities, such as a rejuvenating pool, a leisure area for various activities, and abundant green spaces that add to the beauty of the environment. The community is also securely guarded, offering both privacy and a sense of security. This residence is a perfect mix of comfort, leisure, and protection. Perfectly located near the Air Force Base.
